data.description: Cape cod style home in established neighborhood. Lots of space to spread out or entertain inside and out including the wrap around deck and basement family room/man cave. Owners suite on the main level has deck access and a large bathroom with separate tub and shower. Kitchen has two eating areas including the attached breakfast area or formal dining room. There are two roomy bedrooms upstairs with a hall bathroom. The basement has lots of areas to spread out or make a home office. Welcome home!
